; Coverage test for report.cc lines 942-951
; fn_commodity_price looks up a historical price for a commodity

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $150.00

2024/01/01 Buy stock
    Assets:Brokerage    1 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(commodity_price(amount, date))\n" --limit "account =~ /Brokerage/"
$150.00
end test
